§oTOXIC AVENGER!§r
Mercury and it's ethyl and methyl salts are extremely toxic and have neuro-degenerative effects.
Adding some to a weapon or tool gives it the ability to poison and temporarily blind your enemies.

§oSafety First§r
If you've got some Plutonium or Uranium around and think it'd be great for a weapon, don't forget to add some shielding.
A nice lead plate will stop the deadly radiation from affection you while still letting it harm your enemies.
